Hmm it looks like you saved the file and its missed a tick box for statslist. 

There are two possible workarounds. 

1) Reload your character from the Armoury

2) Open your XML file in a text editor and add the missing line. ie: open the XML file and look for 

  &lt;StatsList&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
  &lt;/StatsList&gt;

and replace it with

  &lt;StatsList&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
  &lt;/StatsList&gt;

ie: add an extra line saying 
    &lt;boolean&gt;true&lt;/boolean&gt;
